          <h2>Six therapeutic domains, 82,000+ claims</h2>
          <p>Robertium pipeline now covers six therapeutic domains: glioblastoma, epilepsy, ALS, Alzheimer's disease, pancreatic cancer, and major depressive disorder. Total: 47,370 papers ingested, 27,177 passed biomedical filtering, 82,708 structured claims extracted across all six domains in the knowledge graph.</p>
          <p>The expansion validates that the methodology works across both oncology and neurology, with cross-domain hypothesis discovery now possible across 30 directional pairs of domains.</p>
